  "title": "Shipping Executive #81007",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Food Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Shipping Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: North - Woodlands (Nearest MRT: Admiralty)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Mon to Fri: 8.30am – 5.30pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3300 + AWS + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare a full set of shipping documents, including BL, Commercial Invoice, Packing List, Insurance, Customs forms, COO, etc. (for LC, sea, and air shipments).</li><li>Apply for SFA Export Health Certificates and Free Sale Certificates.</li><li>Coordinate the courier arrangement for samples and documents.</li><li>Prepare shipping marks as required.</li><li>Ensure all outbound shipment documentation is completed accurately, on time, and in compliance with customer requirements.</li><li>Handle data entry and maintain proper filing of all documents.</li><li>Perform other ad hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. ITE in Logistics or Business Administration</li><li>Min.1 year of working experience in related field</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81007 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
